overview.en: The Dextoken Protocol is a DeFi infrastructure that implements the brand-new Speculative AMM. A unique Price Tick trading mechanism can benefit the crypto ecosystem by mitigating the issue of over-speculation smoothes out strong price fluctuations, a priceless automated market maker that determines the token price based on the volatility.
overview.zh: Dextoken 协议是一种DeFi基础架构，可实现全新的推断性AMM。 独特的Price Tick交易机制可通过缓解过度投机的问题来消除强烈的价格波动，从而使加密生态系统受益，这是种宝贵的自动做市商，可根据波动性确定代币价格。
